01:25.234 --> 01:27.001
911 OPERATOR:
Are those gunshots?

01:27.069 --> 01:29.070
Ma'am, what is your location?
Can you hear me?

01:29.138 --> 01:30.305
You shot 'em, man.

01:30.372 --> 01:32.140
