04:39.112 --> 04:41.146
(stifled sob)

04:42.160 --> 04:43.568
THREDSON:
Everything all right, Sister?

04:46.023 --> 04:49.812
Inclement weather
always upsets the natives.

04:49.932 --> 04:51.208
