05:45.708 --> 05:48.400
But I'll try to locate it.

05:49.484 --> 05:51.691
I'll bet it says he
died of natural causes.

05:51.758 --> 05:54.260
If it's natural for
a 17-year-old boy

05:54.328 --> 05:56.829
to die of a heart attack.

05:56.897 --> 05:59.346
You have quite
a suspicious mind, Sister.

05:59.466 --> 06:01.167
Bordering on delusional.

06:01.235 --> 06:03.469
Or maybe it's just
a form of projection.

06:03.537 --> 06:05.804
A defense to protect

06:05.872 --> 06:07.505
your own guilty conscience.

06:11.176 --> 06:14.344
It was you, wasn't it?

06:14.412 --> 06:17.305
The newspaper, where did you get it?

06:19.062 --> 06:20.850
What newspaper?

06:29.526 --> 06:32.328
That office we gave you--

06:32.396 --> 06:33.696
I need it back.

06:33.764 --> 06:34.964
You've had more than enough time

06:35.031 --> 06:36.465
to advise the courts.

06:36.533 --> 06:38.467
You've got two weeks,

06:38.535 --> 06:39.702
and you're out.

06:52.282 --> 06:54.550
("Dominique" plays)

07:04.127 --> 07:06.161
