arranged for a distraction.

07:23.614 --> 07:27.083
A movie, on Friday night, when
storm will be at its worst.

07:27.151 --> 07:29.153
We're all going to be
together in the dark,

07:29.221 --> 07:31.422
watching <i>The Sign of the Cross,</i>

07:31.490 --> 07:35.993
