Hold your water, Sister.

08:40.558 --> 08:41.893
I'm finishing up something here.

08:41.960 --> 08:43.260
Keep watching, Frank.

08:43.328 --> 08:44.595
Assume the worst.

08:44.663 --> 08:46.898
Roger that, Sister.

08:49.635 --> 08:51.103
What are you doing?

08:51.170 --> 08:53.906
