10:38.978 --> 10:40.645
in order to spy on me.

10:40.713 --> 10:43.548
No, you're wrong.
Was it the Stasi?

10:43.616 --> 10:46.117
The East Germans have a particular
talent for surveillance.

10:46.185 --> 10:47.985
KGB?

10:48.821 --> 10:50.555
