within the U.S government.

10:53.026 --> 10:54.359
Oh, yes.

10:55.728 --> 10:57.596
Jews, and fellow travelers.

10:57.664 --> 10:58.931
Who was it?

10:58.999 --> 11:00.432
It was no one.

11:00.500 --> 11:01.600
