11:03.436 --> 11:07.038
You can swear
all you like, Mr. Walker,

11:07.106 --> 11:08.873
but I will get to the truth.

11:08.941 --> 11:13.277
In here, we have all
the time in the world.

11:13.345 --> 11:15.613
(screaming)

11:28.961 --> 11:31.041
(gasps)

11:35.435 --> 11:37.703
Why are you so fearful, my child?

11:47.152 --> 11:49.120
I can't imagine
what you're so afraid of.

11:49.188 --> 11:51.689
Get on your knees
and we'll pray it all away.

11:51.757 --> 11:54.559
No... no.

12:15.613 --> 12:17.013
