13:31.450 --> 13:33.184
Little Sister.

13:33.252 --> 13:35.320
My ray of sunshine.

13:35.388 --> 13:36.521
Come in.

13:40.193 --> 13:41.493
Please.

13:43.829 --> 13:47.132
