13:53.639 --> 13:55.573
What will happen when it's freezing?

13:57.042 --> 13:58.576
And now this storm?

13:58.644 --> 14:00.545
We only have to get them
through the winter.

14:03.282 --> 14:05.117
I can't tell you
how much your compassion

14:05.184 --> 14:07.152
for these creatures means to me.

14:07.220 --> 14:09.588
Oh, please.

14:09.656 --> 14:11.090
You know you got me in here

14:11.157 --> 14:13.759
