14:19.532 --> 14:20.532
Come on, big boy.

14:20.600 --> 14:22.467
Show me what you got.

14:22.535 --> 14:25.036
A little bride of Christ
has had an awakening.

14:25.104 --> 14:27.772
Not to the Lord...

14:27.840 --> 14:29.474
but to the power of sex...

14:29.541 --> 14:30.508
lust...

14:30.576 --> 14:31.642
desire.

14:31.710 --> 14:32.910
Stop it.

14:32.978 --> 14:36.047
Put your mouth where you want to.

14:36.115 --> 14:37.281
Don't let it go to waste, Doc.

14:37.349 --> 14:38.916
