Thank you, gentlemen.

15:14.487 --> 15:16.722
("Dominique" playing)

15:22.729 --> 15:24.430
Dr. Thredson?

15:24.497 --> 15:25.564
My name

15:25.632 --> 15:26.932
is Lana Winters.

15:27.000 --> 15:28.434
Can I have a word with you?

15:28.501 --> 15:30.502
In private?

15:35.107 --> 15:38.242
Would you excuse us
for a minute, please?

15:38.310 --> 15:40.845
Thank you.

15:44.116 --> 15:46.684
Miss Winters, I know a
little about your case,

15:46.752 --> 15:48.853
but I'm not authorized
to discuss your treatment.

15:48.921 --> 15:50.521
