to evaluate one patient.

15:52.758 --> 15:54.658
No, it's not about me.

15:54.726 --> 15:56.060
I'm going to go out on a limb here.

15:56.128 --> 15:57.762
But I've been watching you,

15:57.829 --> 15:59.163
and I know...

15:59.231 --> 16:01.098
