Wendy Peyser

16:07.572 --> 16:10.775
Your friend-- she's the reason
why you're in here?

16:12.378 --> 16:16.348
She hasn't written or called.

16:16.415 --> 16:18.583
I know Sister Jude is
keeping her away from me.

16:18.651 --> 16:20.619
If I could just see her,

16:20.687 --> 16:23.689
I could straighten this out.

16:23.757 --> 16:25.992
Dr. Thredson...

16:26.060 --> 16:28.828
