17:11.771 --> 17:12.871
I don't know what
you're talking about.

17:13.873 --> 17:16.342
Are we talking to you?

17:16.409 --> 17:18.676
I can help. I'm smart.

17:18.744 --> 17:20.979
Smarter than that
stuck-up bitch reporter.

17:21.047 --> 17:22.012
Come on, Grace.

17:22.080 --> 17:24.616
I got to get out of here.

17:24.684 --> 17:28.053
