17:31.224 --> 17:33.091
I want to go to Paris, France.

17:33.159 --> 17:35.227
They're 20 years ahead of us.

17:35.295 --> 17:37.296
Here, I'm a freak.
There I'd be celebrated.

17:37.364 --> 17:39.399
Haven't you read <i>Delta of Venus?</i>

17:39.466 --> 17:42.669
Anais Nin embraced her sexuality
without apology.

17:42.737 --> 17:44.971
