know what I'm talking about.

17:45.039 --> 17:46.940
We left when I was nine.

17:47.008 --> 17:49.776
But my mother and sister,
we speak French at home.

17:49.844 --> 17:52.212
I'm gonna get out of here
with or without you.

17:52.280 --> 17:54.548
We could help each other.

17:54.616 --> 17:55.783
Please?

17:55.851 --> 17:57.618
(man yells in distance)

17:57.686 --> 18:00.888
MAN: No, no.
ORDERLY: Come on.

18:10.331 --> 18:12.165
Feathering your love nest?

18:14.669 --> 18:16.103
The radio said there was a danger

18:16.171 --> 18:18.606
of the bridge being washed out
by the storm.

18:18.674 --> 18:20.842
I thought it prudent
to spend the night.

18:24.346 --> 18:26.581
Sister Jude, I've had a very long,

18:26.649 --> 18:28.583
particularly strange day.

18:28.651 --> 18:33.054
Whatever it is you wanted,
I'm sure can wait till tomorrow.

18:33.122 --> 18:35.890
"Ravish Me Red"?

18:35.958 --> 18:38.660
(thunder crashes)

18:38.728 --> 18:41.296
