18:53.142 --> 18:55.610
I admired her purity.

18:55.678 --> 18:58.379
Her innocence.

18:58.447 --> 19:00.782
I never had any.

19:00.850 --> 19:02.617
Even as a boy.

19:02.685 --> 19:04.285
Now it's gone.

19:04.353 --> 19:05.920
