19:05.988 --> 19:09.123
Are those tears?

19:09.191 --> 19:11.459
Sister Mary Eunice

19:11.526 --> 19:12.927
has been corrupted.

19:12.995 --> 19:16.130
It's this place.
Those patients.

19:16.198 --> 19:17.832
That loathsome Shelley.

19:17.900 --> 19:19.834
She's a wretched influence.

19:19.901 --> 19:21.768
If she's been corrupted,
it's because of you.

19:21.836 --> 19:24.671
Your leers are quite transparent.

19:24.739 --> 19:27.241
She's a sensitive child.

19:27.308 --> 19:29.877
Your perversion has
awakened something in her

19:29.944 --> 19:31.712
that she can't begin to understand.

19:31.780 --> 19:34.648
